Soil Water Retention Curves

Van Genutchen Equation for soil water retention curves \[ \theta=\theta_{r}+\left(\theta_{s}-\theta_{r}\right)\left[1+(\alpha \psi)^{n}\right]^{-(1-\frac{1}{n})} \]

Van Genutchen Equation for soil water retention curves \[ \psi=\frac{\sqrt[n]{\left(\frac{\theta_{s}-\theta}{\theta_{r}-\theta_{s}}\right)^{n /(n-1)}-1}}{\alpha} \]
